languages.text: "Навигаторы так сильно отождествляют себя с Домом. Должно быть, вам сейчас непросто без опоры на старейшин. Но, даю слово, я позабочусь о вашем благополучии".

traits.locale_text: "Навигаторы так сильно отождествляют себя с Домом. Должно быть, вам сейчас непросто без опоры на старейшин. Но, даю слово, я позабочусь о вашем благополучии".

languages.text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

languages.text: “导航者对家族有着强烈的认同感。你现在无法依靠你的长辈，这对你而言一定很煎熬，但我向你保证，我会照顾好你的。”
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

languages.text: «Los Navegantes se identifican mucho con su casa. Debe de haberle resultado difícil no poder depender de los ancianos. Pero tiene mi palabra de que cuidaré de usted».
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

traits.locale_text: «Los Navegantes se identifican mucho con su casa. Debe de haberle resultado difícil no poder depender de los ancianos. Pero tiene mi palabra de que cuidaré de usted».

languages.text: 「航宙士は己の家を強く意識するものだ。家長に頼ることができないのはつらいことだろう。だが、私がお前の面倒を見ることを約束しよう」
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

traits.locale_text: 「航宙士は己の家を強く意識するものだ。家長に頼ることができないのはつらいことだろう。だが、私がお前の面倒を見ることを約束しよう」

languages.text: "Navigatoren identifizieren sich so stark mit ihrem Haus. Es ist gewiss schwer für Euch, Euch nicht auf Eure Ältesten stützen zu können. Doch Ihr habt mein Wort, dass ich mich um Euch kümmern würde."
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

languages.text: « Les navigateurs sont tellement proches de leur maison. Ce doit être difficile pour vous de ne pas pouvoir vous reposer sur vos aînés. Mais je m'occuperais de vous, je vous en donne ma parole. »
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

languages.text: "Rotacılar, Haneleriyle âdeta özleşmiştir. Hane büyüklerine sırtını dayayamamak senin için zor olmalı. Ama sözüm söz, sana göz kulak olacağım."
languages.original_text: "Navigators identify so strongly with their House. It must be difficult for you not to be able to lean on your elders. But you have my word that I will look after you."

traits.locale_text: "Rotacılar, Hanelerine yakından bağlı oluyor. Hane büyüklerine sırtını dayayamamak senin için zor olmalı. Sözüm söz, sana göz kulak olacağım."
